Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:41.64,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Furom, iestrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.14,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Elmuto... Eril!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:46.23,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Natow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.02,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,显现吧【暴风】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.77,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.90,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 紧绷的大气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.11,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【迷途者】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.57,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,【老绅士】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:09.50,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,这就完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.05,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,投降吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,投降 不！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:13.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:21.91,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.18,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.23,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.69,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Ilm, es, alas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.04,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Schu, limic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.69,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,显现吧 爆破消散之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.17,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,【破坏者】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.79,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,这没完没了的 不愧是乱破师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.11,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:12.27,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,还有什么小伎俩可用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.42,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我还能打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.07,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.80,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,昨天说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.78,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,魔法师的强弱 由经验决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,你缺的是阅历
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.58,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Blow away! The Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:33.50,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:53.19,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,Assa, schron, misam, winhel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.82,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,显现吧【阻御者】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.20,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.86,Default,David,0,0,0,,到此为止了 英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.19,Default,Red,0,0,0,,遗体 交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.54,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎么了 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.47,Default,David,0,0,0,,第一次拿到遗体该高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.96,Default,David,0,0,0,,倒是笑一笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.95,Default,Red,0,0,0,,喜悦 并不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.77,Default,David,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.52,Default,David,0,0,0,,话说回来 还真有点吓人啊…这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.37,Default,Red,0,0,0,,无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲的遗体 神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.10,Default,David,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:43.87,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,真希望 往后都能像这样赶在白丫头之前找到英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.66,Default,David,0,0,0,,嗯 保持这势头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不论精神还是肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.69,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,一旦被雇佣便不会背叛雇主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这是我们唯一的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:07.11,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎么了 莫非是想起那个乱破师小子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.85,Default,Red,0,0,0,,否定 坚决否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.44,Default,David,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.44,Default,David,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.12,Default,David,0,0,0,,很危险啊 我可在驾马车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.15,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,谁让你说话不经大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.07,Default,Red,0,0,0,,遗体 收集的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:25.22,Default,Red,0,0,0,,白色的冒牌女儿 父亲 凭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.57,Default,Red,0,0,0,,目的 实在明确
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.42,Default,Red,0,0,0,,相对 我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,复仇 模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.96,Default,Red,0,0,0,,具体内容 难以掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.27,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,这估计…集齐后就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.38,Default,David,0,0,0,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以咱就尽可能多地收集这玩意…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.67,Default,Red,0,0,0,,无礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:47.97,Default,David,0,0,0,,知道啦 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:51.69,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.14,Default,Red,0,0,0,,奇伊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.65,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,拿到了吗 贾兹皇帝的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.36,Default,David,0,0,0,,又突然冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:09.58,Default,David,0,0,0,,我们正好想赶超那个白色丫头和乱破师兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.00,Default,David,0,0,0,,下个遗体在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.30,Default,David,0,0,0,,你是带情报来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.46,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.87,Default,Red,0,0,0,,地点 说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:19.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,从这里朝海岸方向走一天有个渔村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.40,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,叫克里·摩根的英雄在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.92,Default,Red,0,0,0,,抓紧前往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.85,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,不用这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.76,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,我还有个情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.35,Default,Red,0,0,0,,说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:32.22,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,远海的小岛 不妨一去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:33.85,Default,Red,0,0,0,,岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.24,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,没准会遇到好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:44.30,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,基列特队长的遗物 继续保持在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.49,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,我希望队长回来随时都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.04,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,所以 队名也保持基列特队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.69,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,嗯 我听机关长说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.17,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.26,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,这样下去没法反击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.86,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,陷阱的状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.22,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,几乎全被拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.18,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁 阿卡莉 投降 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.60,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,完全无法近身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.61,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,慢人一手只能被动挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我去当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,诱饵 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,躲在这也只会跟石头一起被炸飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.37,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不成功便成仁 只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.47,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:38.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我尽量分散她的注意 阿卡莉从反方向进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.52,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡别急 先找个能保证射击的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,成功率第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好 行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾即为钢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.69,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾钢故无畏 吾钢故无惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:57.23,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,若敌当前 便舍弃一切顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾乃灭敌之凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.79,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,铁血转化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.45,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,想抄我后路？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:14.99,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Alay, salama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.54,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,没错嘉依卡 就这样继续
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.67,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Sabah, amasala, missah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.71,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:36.85,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.68,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.99,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Salimic, binnu, alay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.02,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 冲击粉碎之物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【重击者】
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.48,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.98,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾乃凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.88,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁 没问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:36.36,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.61,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.43,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.33,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 胜过一招 已经确保
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.85,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是啊 赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.01,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,想做还是能做到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.15,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.67,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,不只是因为那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.39,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,没发觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:08.95,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,刚刚你想全力保护他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:14.03,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,魔法攻击的威力 关键就看魔法师的思绪有多强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.51,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.37,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,果然你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.63,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,看你就是皇帝的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,理解 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.55,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,啊啦 它是你养的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.01,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:47.83,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,珂罗蒂雅女士 到约定的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不懂风情 我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:54.79,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,是 但非常抱歉 请尽快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.15,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,工作堆积很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.12,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,总之先喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,这点时间没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.18,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,期待 喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.01,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,想吃各种葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:24.18,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,【深夜中拔出的剑 无法再收回鞘中】
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.02,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,听不太懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.33,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.86,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不过签上所说 我会谨记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.78,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,薇薇的写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.57,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,我的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:40.22,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,【想拯救所爱之人 要用你不变的爱】
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:45.46,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.89,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是基列特队长的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.63,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,在【四月号】里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:59.41,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,刚才 我跟尼克拉队长确认了内容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:04.68,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,与嘉依卡和贾兹皇帝相关的疑问及考察 记得密密麻麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:10.95,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,队长有多么关心嘉依卡一案 全都体现在这笔记上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:18.25,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,这里 主要保管着从贾兹帝国城押收的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:22.03,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,其实 我也没详细调查过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:25.94,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,正如笔记中所写
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:31.00,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,他那样的魔法师 没留下任何魔法技术资料 实在不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:35.10,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,于是 我重新查阅了这里的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.96,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,找到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.93,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,贾兹皇帝讨伐队的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:45.80,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,遗产？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.56,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,卡莲小姐 这个可以交给我保管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.00,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让你看就是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:58.65,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,我会继续调查这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:02.36,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,希望你像往常一样 继续追捕嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.83,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,是 我做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.48,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,康拉德机关长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.18,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,什么事 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.88,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,我跟薇薇聊过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.11,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:43.96,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,战争结束多年 居然还会这样痛失部下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:44.69,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.91,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,亚伯力克的见解或许该多重视下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:50.85,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.29,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,那么 薇薇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.18,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是 她很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.41,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,另外 机关长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.72,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,最近 烟抽的有点多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.65,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,一点粗陋之物 还请尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.61,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,葡萄 格外甜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.28,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,新鲜葡萄 全部绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.42,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,把那个拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.24,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.01,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,这是说好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.63,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父亲的遗体？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:36.79,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.02,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你没用过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.18,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,遗体吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:40.67,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:45.50,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,战后五年间就建了这么大的葡萄园和酒窖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.14,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,还以为肯定把皇帝遗体当思念料用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:53.78,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嘛 这我也不是没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:57.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,用它做葡萄酒味道肯定有保证
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.33,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,但是 总有点抵触
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.99,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你…跟我们之前遇到的英雄不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:06.77,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:11.51,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嘛 讨伐队成员中 怪癖的人本来就多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:15.25,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,战争一结束 有很多人流落街头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:20.31,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,我不想变成那样 所以有了人生目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:24.95,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,而且 虽然作为英雄拿了遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.07,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,但那不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:31.39,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,听说叫嘉依卡的女孩在收集遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.11,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,就绝对【如果看着顺眼就送给她】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.81,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,遗体放在我这 毕竟不如放在女儿那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:40.77,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.71,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,对了 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,知道遗产的所在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:45.88,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,遗产？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,遗产 存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.53,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,啊啦 你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:53.59,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,贾兹城陷落时 魔法师残党说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.94,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,皇帝有份遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.88,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,求你们 请你饶我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.84,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,我用情报作交换
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:15.44,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,我知道贾兹皇帝的重要机密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:16.34,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:22.06,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,接到贾兹皇帝旨意的魔法师 不久前调去了国外的孤岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:26.15,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,那里藏有皇帝的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,谢谢你的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:38.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,但是我们 奉命歼灭贾兹城内所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:41.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,即便是一只老鼠 也不可放过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:50.68,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,讨伐队的记录人员 将秘密和皇帝遗产一事 都上报了联合军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.22,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,皇帝的遗产 如今何处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.23,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,虽然联合军着手调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.34,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,结果什么都没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:03.82,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,什么都？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.44,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,然后调查就被腰斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.56,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,破城后把城内翻了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:14.41,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,但魔法技术相关的实验道具和资料 一件都没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:21.69,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,大推测 贾兹皇帝派出的魔法师 把这些东西都带上了孤岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,岛 父亲的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.63,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,不过遗体能还给你就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.90,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.88,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,还要继续旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:32.76,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.88,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那…可能有遗体的地方 我给你写出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你知道在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.53,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其余英雄的名字和出身地罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.27,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,还剩这么多 别客气快点吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.50,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,我只记得大概 而且都过了五年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.64,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,不知如今还在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.29,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,这样一来 进度能加快不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:58.07,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯 可以跟撞大运的旅行说拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.81,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.59,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:11.84,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,都大半夜了还启程 再住一晚多好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,毕竟是我们来打搅的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.97,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,至少喝杯葡萄酒再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我对酒没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.59,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,葡萄酒能滋润人生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.40,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这是酒鬼的说辞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.81,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,等你懂了这说辞 记得回来很找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.40,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,等我懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.86,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,承蒙照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,礼物 大量 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.70,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,珂罗蒂雅的葡萄 绝品 不可能忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.07,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.94,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,交给那个不知真假的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.20,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,对您而言明明是勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.88,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那不是什么勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个摆设
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.57,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,现在我眼中的勋章…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是今年的葡萄酒 能卖个更好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.55,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.31,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,怎么了 做恶梦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,凄惨的记忆 斩首的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是那个记忆 假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是真的 我已经死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:55.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我自己 冒牌的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.14,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,在那之前 我 什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.17,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 复数存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:05.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,皇帝真正的女儿 有传言已死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我的记忆 混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,胸中不安 心烦意乱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.76,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,确实 你会这样想也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,但是 这不影响你的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:24.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,目的 遗体收集 父亲 凭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.13,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,所以 只能向着它前进啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:33.08,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我和阿卡莉 都一心要为主人你达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.72,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这不就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.25,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,没错 我也这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.53,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,天也亮了 咱们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你 是八英雄之一 葛伦·冬克沃特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.86,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,嘛 是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.38,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,你们 身手不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.54,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,把皇帝的遗体交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.24,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,这个嘛…遗体已经不在我这了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:08.98,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.73,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,昨天 交给一个红色丫头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:13.94,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,红色？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.24,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,红嘉依卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.33,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嘉依卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.60,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,他们也还在收集遗体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.85,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,离我们应该不远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:33.16,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,剩下就是亚兰·托拉蒙塔纳子爵 史蒂芬·哈尔特根 科林·摩根吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可别被红嘉依卡抢了先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:37.96,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父亲的岛 寻找 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:48.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,找到它 我 什么人 理解可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.33,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.69,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:54.45,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,解明疑惑 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.83,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,居住港口城市的英雄 魁梧的枪兵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.13,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,工头 很强 困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:35.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 海上故事 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.39,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是 在此之前 战斗不可避免
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.83,Title,Chaika,0,0,0,,下集 若梦迷心之港
